g" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/MissingChildren" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MissingChildren&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110525143944996721</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jun 2023 10:37:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Q ✨ @ GPN</title><link>https://glauca.space/@q/110519816852282903</link><description>OH: “it’s called a commit because my code is a crime”</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110526087869070366</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jun 2023 14:37:40 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Nonya Bidniss</title><link>https://mas.to/@Nonya_Bidniss/110525949687811019</link><description>The Carrington event of 1859 disrupted telegraph lines. A “Miyake event” would be far worseResearch into tree rings has revealed "Miyake events" ... cosmic events of significantly greater intensity...“Those two scintillating days in 1859 are barely a blip” ...A Miyake event would cripple modern society&lt;a href="https://bigthink.com/hard-science/miyake-event-worse-carrington-event/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;bigthink.com/hard-science/miya&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;ke-event-worse-carrington-event/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110526113706149533</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jun 2023 14:44:14 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Duke</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@DukeDuke/110521261180663419</link><description>With all the talk about Dumb Donnie's indictment for espionage, we seem to be forgetting a key issue. He was elected into his security clearance. There's no way in ten hells he ever would've received one if he had to go through the same process as the rest of us. That is a monstrous problem and no one is addressing it.&lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/USPol" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;USPol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Trump" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Trump&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Espionage" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Espionage&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">110526145228275790</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jun 2023 14:52:15 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>